title: 'Survivor' Season 43 Premiere
description:
Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee return for Season 43 of 'Survivor' and are joined by Johnny Bananas to help recap the premiere episode. Johnny discusses the different strategies he sees and how 'Survivor' compares to 'The Challenge.' They also go through all the tribes, the need for a villain on the show, the difference between hosts Jeff Probst and T.J. Lavin, and so much more.
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Johnny Bananas
Producers: Jessie Lopez and Kai Grady
